Subject: [FD] NULL pointer dereference in glXGetDrawableScreen() of OpenGL
	libglvnd

[Vulnerability description]
OpenGL libglvnd bb06db5a was discovered to contain a NULL pointer dereference via the function glXGetDrawableScreen().

[Vulnerability Type]
Buffer Overflow

[Vendor of Product]
OpenGL

[Affected Product Code Base]
libglvnd - bb06db5a

[Reference]
https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/glvnd/libglvnd/-/issues/242

[CVE Reference]
The Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures project (cve.mitre.org) has assigned the name CVE-2023-45924 to this vulnerability.
